@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000



### Fetch reviews — valid URL (Cookie Run: OvenBreak)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/fetch
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.devsisters.cos"
}


### Fetch and analyze — default prompts (no custom instructions)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/fetch-and-analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.devsisters.cos",
    "sort": "newest"
}


### Fetch and analyze — with custom instructions
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/fetch-and-analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.devsisters.cos",
    "sort": "newest",
    "sentiment_instructions": "Reviews about pricing alone should be neutral, not negative. Reviews that mention both positives and negatives should lean toward the dominant tone.",
    "priority_instructions": "Pay special attention to crash reports, login issues, and data loss. Performance complaints about lag or slow loading are NOT high priority unless they make the app unusable."
}

